🐍 Python Beginner Notes

📌 What is Python?
Python is a general-purpose programming language
It is simple, readable, and beginner-friendly
Used in AI, web development, cybersecurity, automation, and more

🚀 Common Uses of Python
1. Data Science & Machine Learning
Data analysis and AI model building
Libraries:
Pandas → Data analysis
NumPy → Numerical operations
TensorFlow / Scikit-learn → Machine Learning

2. Web Development
Backend development for websites
Frameworks:
Django
FastAPI
Flask
Used by Instagram, Pinterest, etc.

3. Cybersecurity
Malware detection
Security automation
Threat analysis

4. IoT & Embedded Systems
Runs on Raspberry Pi and microcontrollers
Used in:
Smart homes
Sensors
IoT devices
5. DevOps
CI/CD automation scripts
Server monitoring
Infrastructure management

6. Software Testing
Automated testing tools
Example: pytest

7. Automation
File handling
Email automation
Web scraping

Libraries:
Selenium → Browser automation
BeautifulSoup → Web scraping

⭐ Why Learn Python?
Easy to learn
Powerful and flexible
High industry demand
Beginner-friendly
